#EveryLifeMatters
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Over the last few weeks, there have been countless individuals and organizations that have rallied to help their fellow citizens as we face the devastating effects of the 2nd wave of this pandemic.

Seeing these individuals in action, doing such inspiring work, is heart warming and I feel we need to do our best to support them in whatever way we can. Which is why I have partnered with @kettoindia to start the #EveryLifeMatters initiative.

Through this initiative we plan to raise funds to help individuals in dire need of financial support for medical treatment, and also provide support to amplify the work of the countless covid heroes out there who are doing their level best to help.

I urge you all to help in whatever way you can, because together we can make a difference!

Our cover girl Diana Penty (@dianapenty) didn’t chase the spotlight. It found her. Already a successful model, she walked into what she thought was a quick meeting and walked out with her debut role in Cocktail. Shy and a little unsure, she said yes anyway. And just like that, her journey in film began.

For our May cover, Diana brought the same quiet confidence and natural ease. No fuss, no filters, just her being completely herself. We captured her in her element and every shot felt effortless and full of soul.

Thank you Diana for your warmth, your grace, and for bringing your beautiful energy to every moment on set.🌼
